// Game2D — 15-puzzle with 2D nested array storage [[u256; 4]; 4]
//
// Board is stored as a 4x4 grid accessed via (row, col) coordinates.
// Adjacency is computed from coordinates (no lookup table needed).
//
// Fe features exercised: nested array storage [[u256; 4]; 4],
// 2D indexing board[row][col], coordinate arithmetic, while loops.
// =============================================================================

